==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Eradication
<hw>E*rad`i*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>eradicatio</ets>: cf. F. <ets>⟦eacute⟧radication</ets>.]</ety>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of plucking up by the roots; a rooting out;
extirpation; utter destruction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The state of being plucked up by the
roots.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eradicative</ent>⟦br⟧
